description: The Lowepro Rezo 60 offers a sophisticated, lightweight design that disguises serious protection for digital camera. It includes many features found in larger bags: zippered compartments; inner pockets for memory, batteries or small accessories; SlipLock attachment tab and adjustable shoulder strap.Capacity: Large digital or 35mm camera, memory cards, batteries or small accessoriesSize (interior, W x D x H): 3 x 2.75 x 5.5 inches / 7.5 x 7 x 14 centimeters (stretches)Outer fabric: Water-resistant microfiber and ripstop nylon with stretch gusset
title: Lowepro Rezo 60 Camera Case (Black)
